Extend Your Customer 360 Experiences with Heroku

Explore how Heroku provides the tools and infrastructure to meet your diverse business requirements. With flexible deployment options, auto-scaling capabilities, extensive add-ons, and reference apps, developers can innovate with performance and security in mind.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Developer, Enterprise, Professional, Starter, and Unlimited editions.

How: From Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Heroku, and then select About Heroku.
